  "title": "3 spherical UFOs followed a passenger plane for 15 minutes near Fortaleza [2013]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/02/3-spherical-ufos-followed-a-passenger-plane-for-15-minutes-near-fortaleza-2013/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-5n",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>FEB 13th, 2013.</strong> At the end of the flight that left Manaus for Fortaleza, a pilot reported that 80 nautical miles to reach Fortaleza Airport, at an altitude of 28,000 ft, they spotted 3 luminous spheres following their aircraft. The report was made, according to the file consulted, through the telephone with the ACC-RE [in Recife]. The unidentified flying objects moved at approximately 700 km/h, and they were yellow in color, and spherical in shape. The sighting lasted about 15 minutes and happened at 4:40 am under good weather conditions.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.716. &#8220;<span class=\"s1\" style=\"color:#808000;\"><span class=\"s1\"><i>Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado (ovni) em Fortaleza, Ceará.</i></span></span>&#8220;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n",
